<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Profile Update Required</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%);">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%); padding: 40px 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: #1E293B; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3); box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);">
          
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F59E0B 0%, #EF4444 50%, #8B5CF6 100%); padding: 50px 40px; text-align: center;">
              <div style="width: 90px; height: 90px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 20px; backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4); line-height: 90px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
                <span style="font-size: 45px;">üìù</span>
              </div>
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Profile Update Required</h1>
              <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500;">Action needed to publish your profile</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Content -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 50px 40px;">
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15) 0%, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15) 100%); border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; padding: 25px; margin: 0 0 35px; border-radius: 12px;">
                <p style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 700;">
                  Hi <span style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #F59E0B, #EF4444); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;">{{name}}</span>,
                </p>
                <p style="color: #CBD5E1; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7;">
                  Your candidate profile has been reviewed. A few updates are needed before we can publish it. Don't worry - we'll guide you through the changes!
                </p>
              </div>

              <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 35px;">
                Our review team has provided specific feedback to help you improve your profile. Please review the details below and make the necessary updates.
              </p>

              {{#if reason}}
              <!-- Feedback Box -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%); border: 2px solid #EF4444; border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 35px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                  <div style="width: 40px; height: 40px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EF4444, #F59E0B); border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 15px;">üí¨</div>
                  <h3 style="color: #FCA5A5; font-size: 16px; margin: 0; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Feedback from Review Team</h3>
                </div>
                <div style="background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1); border-left: 3px solid #EF4444; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
                  <p style="color: #FED7D7; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7;">{{reason}}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              {{/if}}

              <!-- Action Steps -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 0%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1) 100%); border-radius: 16px; padding: 35px 30px; margin-bottom: 35px;">
                <h3 style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 25px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center;">‚úÖ How to Fix This</h3>
                
                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 18px 0;">
                      <div style="display: flex; align-items: start;">
                        <div style="width: 35px; height: 35px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B5CF6, #06B6D4); border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 35px; font-weight: 800; color: white; font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 15px;">1</div>
                        <div>
                          <p style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 5px; font-weight: 700;">Log In to Your Portal</p>
                          <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">Access your candidate dashboard</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 18px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);">
                      <div style="display: flex; align-items: start;">
                        <div style="width: 35px; height: 35px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06B6D4, #10B981); border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 35px; font-weight: 800; color: white; font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 15px;">2</div>
                        <div>
                          <p style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 5px; font-weight: 700;">Review the Feedback</p>
                          <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">Carefully read the review team's comments</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 18px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);">
                      <div style="display: flex; align-items: start;">
                        <div style="width: 35px; height: 35px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10B981, #F59E0B); border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 35px; font-weight: 800; color: white; font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 15px;">3</div>
                        <div>
                          <p style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 5px; font-weight: 700;">Make the Updates</p>
                          <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">Apply the necessary corrections to your profile</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 18px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);">
                      <div style="display: flex; align-items: start;">
                        <div style="width: 35px; height: 35px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F59E0B, #8B5CF6); border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 35px; font-weight: 800; color: white; font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 15px;">4</div>
                        <div>
                          <p style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 5px; font-weight: 700;">Submit for Re-Review</p>
                          <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">We'll review it promptly and get you published</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </div>

              <!-- CTA Button -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 35px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="{{profileUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F59E0B 0%, #EF4444 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 20px 60px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 17px; box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">
                      Update Your Profile ‚Üí
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Pro Tip -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 100%); border-left: 4px solid #06B6D4; padding: 25px; margin-top: 35px; border-radius: 12px;">
                <p style="color: #67E8F9; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 700;">
                  üí° Pro Tip
                </p>
                <p style="color: #A5F3FC; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7;">
                  Ensure all required fields are complete and accurate. High-quality photos and detailed descriptions significantly improve your approval chances!
                </p>
              </div>

              <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 35px 0 0;">
                Need assistance? Our support team is here to help!<br>
                Email: <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #F59E0B; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">{{supportEmail}}</a>
              </p>

              <p style="color: #CBD5E1; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 30px 0 0;">
                We're rooting for you!<br>
                <strong style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #F59E0B, #EF4444); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; font-size: 18px;">The ITFY E-Voting Team</strong>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);">
              <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 10px;">
                <a href="{{profileUrl}}" style="color: #F59E0B; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Candidate Portal</a> | 
                <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #06B6D4; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Contact Support</a>
              </p>
              <p style="color: #64748B; font-size: 12px; margin: 10px 0 0;">
                ¬© {{formatDate currentYear}} ITFY E-Voting. All rights reserved.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>